node.text: On the plus side, the dishes are done. 💁🏻‍♀️

Here is a true story about me getting a tattoo. A short documentary film, by me. It will be on my body forever and I couldn’t be more happy about it. Thank you @beauxbrady 🔪 @portcitytattooca 🔪 (and thank you @jessiexlee for the referral) 🤟
